        public boolean processTSV(File file,
                          IExperimentalDesignReader reader,
                          boolean parseGraph)
                   throws IOException,
                          JAXBException
        Reads in a TSV File containing samples for openBIS registration and their metadata.
        Parameters:
        file - A TSV File that must contain Identifier, space, project, experiment and sample type of each sample and optionally the parents of each sample. Additional metadata columns must be known to openBIS and fit to the sample type in question.
        designType -
        Throws:
        IOException
        JAXBException

      • getProcessed

        public List<List<life.qbic.datamodel.samples.ISampleBean>> getProcessed()
        Returns a nested list structure of all processed samples to be registered, using TSVSampleBeans. The outer list sorts samples by their hierarchy (parent-child-structure of openBIS), beginning with the highest samples.
        Returns:
        Nested list of samples to be registered, sorted by hierarchy level and sample type.
